<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="Dumbbell-Chest-Fly">Dumbbell Chest Fly</h3>



<p>The <a href="https://www.endomondo.com/exercise/dumbbell-chest-fly" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">dumbbell chest fly</a> is a key exercise to include in an effective <a href="https://www.endomondo.com/exercise/chest-workout-routine" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">chest workout routine</a>. It targets the chest and upper arms, contributing to a balanced and sculpted upper body.</p>



<p>It is a great addition to womenâ€™s upper-body workouts because it isolates the chest muscles for balanced upper-body development. It also improves core stability as you engage to keep your back straight when moving through the range of motion.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-vimeo wp-block-embed-vimeo wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio vimeo-custom"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper">
